---
title: Easy Chicken Korma Curry with Rapid Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: There's nothing like mildly-spiced curry made with creamy coconut milk for a warming weeknight meal. Make sure to use the fluffy rice to soak up all that delicious goodness!
